/*** Pinout used on a 8-way cable:
Function      Pin   WireColor
GND           GND   DarkBrown
RainSensor    D6    LightBrown
TempHumSensor D7    LightGreen
WiFiRx        D4    LightBlue
WiFiTx        D5    DarkBlue
